===發行與反響===
《想念你》於2000年12月第2週派往美國拉丁電台發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TxEEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA36&dq=intitle:billboard+%22pero+me+acuerdo+de+ti%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=XA1-UZ7SJIm49gTm8oGQDg&ved=0CDkQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Christina On Top|last=Cobo|first=Leila|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2000-12-23|accessdate=2013-04-29|volume=112|issue=52|page=35|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203223001/http://books.google.com/books?id=TxEEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA36&dq=intitle:billboard+%22pero+me+acuerdo+de+ti%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=XA1-UZ7SJIm49gTm8oGQDg&ved=0CDkQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲在{{tsl|en|Hot Latin Songs|熱門拉丁歌曲榜|熱門拉丁歌曲榜}}和{{tsl|en|Latin Pop Airplay|拉丁流行電台歌曲榜|拉丁流行電台歌曲榜}}分別最高排第8與第5。<ref name=bill/>在西班牙，歌曲則最高取得了季軍。<ref name=spainchart/>{{tsl|en|Wall of Sound (record label)|聲墻 (唱片廠牌)|聲墻}}的庫特·B·瑞利對歌曲持正面評價，稱阿奎萊拉在歌曲中“令人信服且具吸引力”。<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20001017104843/http://wallofsound.go.com/reviews/stories/mireflejo_christinaaguileraIndex.html|url=http://wallofsound.go.com/reviews/stories/mireflejo_christinaaguileraIndex.html|title=Wall of Sound Review: Mi Reflejo|publisher={{tsl|en|Wall of Sound|聲墻 (唱片廠牌)|Wall of Sound}}|archivedate=2000-10-17|accessdate=2013-11-28}}</ref>《{{tsl|en|Orlando Sentinel|奧蘭多衛報|奧蘭多衛報}}》的編輯派瑞·盖特曼則寫道：“她看起來同樣喜歡（高音）炫技顫音和性挑逗般的低音呻吟”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2000-09-15/entertainment/0009150025_1_aguilera-mariah-carey-mi-reflejo|title=Aguilera Must Not Know Spanish Word For Subtlety|first=Parry|last=Gettelman|work={{tsl|en|Orlando Sentinel|奧蘭多衛報|Orlando Sentinel}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Tribune Company|論壇媒體|Tribune Company}}|date=2000-09-15|accessdate=2013-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021063947/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2000-09-15/entertainment/0009150025_1_aguilera-mariah-carey-mi-reflejo|archivedate=2013-10-21}}</ref>在第2屆[[拉丁格莱美奖|拉丁格莱美奖]]，《想念你》獲得了「{{tsl|en|Latin Grammy Award for Record of the Year|拉丁格莱美奖年度制作|年度制作}}」提名，但敗給了[[亞雷漢德羅·桑斯|亞雷漢德羅·桑斯]]的《{{lang|es|El Alma al Aire}}》。<ref name="lgnom2001">{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2001/jul/18/entertainment/ca-23444|title=The Full List of Nominations|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Tribune Company|date=2001-07-18|accessdate=2013-04-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026135501/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/jul/18/entertainment/ca-23444|archivedate=2012-10-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/77905/sanz-juanes-top-winners-at-2nd-latin-grammys|title=Sanz, Juanes Top Winners At 2nd Latin Grammys|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2013-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131022158/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/77905/sanz-juanes-top-winners-at-2nd-latin-grammys|archivedate=2014-01-31}}</ref>

===宣傳===
